{"tid":266692,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得同一時間whatsapp多過一個人傾計好辛苦","createTime":"2017-06-01T16:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T16:44:43.000Z","uid":30259,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81087a8eb05f83e3a320fa260c4f97b1b28b5457","tid":266692,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:12:42.000Z","msg":"如果同一時間有不停有人搵你，例如A君 B君 C君 D君，E君，唔係群組，係單對單傾，狂彈藍色數字圈好有壓力，覆完呢個A又要覆另一個B，又要諗點覆，諗完點覆A又要諗點覆B，有時又收到A一大篇字海又唔好意思覆幾隻字，跟住點都要諗點覆番多D字數比A，結果秒回唔到B，又比B罵我遲覆，跟住覆完B，仲要諗點覆C，覆完C又要覆D，覆完D又要覆E，覆完E都又要覆番A，無限loop，最慘係佢地如果知個都秒回，都唔敢靜太耐先覆，結果完全做唔到自己野。。"},{"pid":"eef79dee6c9b74b678672a35ecbf6340231d6ad1","tid":266692,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"好羨慕有人可以同時同十個人單對單傾whatsapp都可以面不改容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383a374f161bfa8e0359551dd817be0230431b01","tid":266692,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:18:06.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n好耐無試過同幾條仔WhatsApp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c2a3dfca02160af4617f1e01c7fdbcab536014","tid":266692,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<br />\n好耐無試過同幾條仔WhatsApp <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔怕send左野比人?"},{"pid":"b0bf5ba9415a8b1395314a86b05d088fc92eec1a","tid":266692,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"其實覆兩個已經好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d83e712a797ce7db45a7c5f974189c47b68e24","tid":266692,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實覆兩個已經好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做唔到其他野"},{"pid":"defc80067bf2e8705a88b72ebd1c827a9d81a2c7","tid":266692